{"id":106519,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":8,"day":10}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"半周画刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"206","ytitle":"","mtitle":"三峡","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸猿声啼不住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻舟已过万重山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜甫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡，是长江上险要的峭壁，下面湍急着流水，要形容其险要，简直是同瀑布从山缝里滚下的急遽一样，不过这瀑布是斜倾在江心，而不是吊在空中罢了。然而，这么一泻千里湍急的江水，就飘浮着沉重的木船，载着无数的飞不了，行不得的抗战“归客”。三峡大抵是离渝十天的水程碑了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三峡夹岸之归州城</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三峡下之激流</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>绝壁上之栈道</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三峡中之风箱峡</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>六十三滩上之民船</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三峡上流夔府之盐泉</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>巫山之盐舟</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1946\\08\\468a060108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三峡断崖上之钟乳洞民居</FONT>"}]}